I live in Tokyo.(我住在东京。) 
Are you here on vacation? (您是来度假的吗? )
I'm here on business.(我是来工作的。) 
How long have you been in Japan? (您来日本多长时间了?)
About four months. (4个月左右。 )
Are you used to life in Japan? (你习惯日本的生活了吗?)
How long will you be in Japan? (你在日本呆到什么时候?)
Until December. (呆到12月。 )
Do you speak Japanese? (你说日语吗?)
A little.(只会一点儿。 )
I can't speak Japanese at all. (我一点儿都不会说。) 
