You knew that, didn't you?（你知道的吧? ）
It is as if I had done something wrong. （好像是我做错了什么事似的。）
He chickened out at the last moment. （他在最后关头胆怯了。 ）
Don't take it out on me. （别冲我发火。）
Pay up! (还我钱!)
You'll pay for this. （我会找你算帐的。 ）
You're out of your mind! （你疯了! ）
You shouldn't say things like that.（你怎么这么说? ）
It's for your own good! (这可全为了你!)
Why are you picking on me? (你干吗老挑我的刺儿?) 
He always finds fault with my work.（他对我的工作总是鸡蛋里挑骨头。）
●制止
Hold it! （停! ）
Wait!（等等! ）
Uh-uh-uh! （别动!别动! ）
