It drives me crazy.(简直快让我疯了。 )
Is that all? (就这些吗?)
That's not enough. (这太少了。/这不够。 )
He's unfair to me. (他对我不公平。 )
●发怒
No more excuses!(别再辩解了! )
I've heard enough of your excuses. (我不想再听你的辩解了。) 
I don't want to hear any excuses.(我不想听任何解释。) 
