I'm serious. (我是认真的。)
Take my word for it.(这是真的呀! )
You'd better believe it! (请相信! )
I'm sure of it.(我敢肯定。 )
It may sound strange, but it's true. (听起来也许奇怪，但它是真的。)
I'm innocent!(我是无辜的! )

 
21 怀 疑  时
