I won't buy that story. (我不信他的话。)
Do you think she's serious?(你认为她是当真的吗? )
I don't take him too seriously.(我不把他的话太当真。 )
I don't believe him. (我不相信他。)
It's too good to be true. (有这么好的事!)

 
22  为 难  时
