Should I wear a jacket and tie? (我必须得穿外衣打领带吗? )
Should the ladies wear dresses? (女性必须穿礼服吗? )
How many in your group? (请问您几位?)
Two. (2个人。 )
I'm sorry, but I have to cancel my reservation.(对不起，我想取消订餐。)
●点菜
